QVD-L7R

The QVD L7R ("level-7 router") is a network server that accepts connections
from QVD clients and forwards them to desktop sessions that run on virtual
machines.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc QVD::L7R

You can also look for information at:

      QVD home page
          http://qvd.morfeo-project.org
      
      QVD blog
          http://qvdblog.qindel.com

